      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Luca Hemmerich</b>\n</p><p><b>Luca Hemmerich</b>,<br />\na German chess player and programmer. He was active in computer chess programming in 2009 and 2010 so far, when he developed his chess engine <a href=\"/ChessMind\" title=\"ChessMind\">ChessMind</a> at age 15 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Hemmerich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Hemmerich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29873\">Null-moves and zugzwang</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29905\">Extensions/Reductions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30695\">Winning percentage and centipawns</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Advantage,_Win_Percentage,_and_Elo\" title=\"Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo\">Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=305218\">Transposition table pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010\">2010</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Hemmerich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32046\">bitScanReverse32</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32345\">Problems when implementing checks in qsearch</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search#Checks\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Checks in Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32348\">TT score</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32984\">Problems with LMR in late endgames</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 01, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=33868\">WAC.002 by evaluation?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 18, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Connected_Passed_Pawns\" title=\"Connected Passed Pawns\">Connected Passed Pawns</a>, <a href=\"/Win_at_Chess\" title=\"Win at Chess\">Win at Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34066\">New UCI engine: ChessMind</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 29, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34711\">ChessMind 0.82</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  June 04, 2010</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Hemmerich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=12918890\">Hemmerich, Luca - FIDE Chess Profile</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luca_Hemmerich&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55596&amp;start=1\">Re: Youngest author of an original engine?</a> by <a href=\"/Adam_Hair\" title=\"Adam Hair\">Adam Hair</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34066\">New UCI engine: ChessMind</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Luca Hemmerich</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 29, 2010</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228190809\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nE